title: Seretide
description: Seretide is a medication used to treat asthma and chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD). It contains two active ingredients: fluticasone propionate and salmeterol. Fluticasone propionate is a corticosteroid that reduces inflammation in the airways, while salmeterol is a long-acting beta agonist that helps to relax the muscles of the airways, making breathing easier.

title: Fish oil
description: Fish oil supplements contain omega-3 fatty acids, which are essential nutrients that are important for maintaining heart health. Omega-3 fatty acids have been shown to reduce inflammation, lower blood pressure, and improve overall cardiovascular health. They may also have benefits for brain health and may help to reduce the risk of certain chronic diseases.

title: Vitamin C 990mg
description: Vitamin C supplements are commonly taken to support immune function and overall health. They may help to reduce the duration and severity of colds and may also have antioxidant properties that protect cells from damage caused by free radicals. Vitamin C is essential for collagen production, wound healing, and the absorption of iron from plant-based foods.

title: Sudafed
description: Sudafed is a decongestant medication used to relieve nasal congestion caused by colds, allergies, or sinus infections. It works by narrowing the blood vessels in the nasal passages, which reduces swelling and congestion. Sudafed is available in both oral and nasal spray forms and is typically used for short-term relief of congestion.

title: Vitamin C
description: Vitamin C is an essential nutrient that plays a key role in immune function, wound healing, and collagen production. It is found naturally in many fruits and vegetables, but supplements are commonly taken to ensure adequate intake, especially during times of illness or stress. Vitamin C may also have antioxidant properties that protect cells from damage.

title: Aspirin
description: Aspirin is a nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug (NSAID) commonly used to relieve pain, reduce inflammation, and lower fever. It is also used in low doses as a blood thinner to reduce the risk of heart attack and stroke in people at high risk. Aspirin works by inhibiting the production of prostaglandins, which are chemicals that promote inflammation, pain, and fever.

title: Collagen
description: Collagen is a protein that provides structure to the skin, hair, nails, bones, and connective tissues. It is the most abundant protein in the body and is essential for maintaining healthy skin elasticity and hydration. Collagen supplements are commonly taken to improve skin health, reduce wrinkles, and promote joint health. They may also support muscle growth and repair.

title: Digene
description: Digene is an antacid medication used to relieve symptoms of indigestion, heartburn, and acid reflux. It works by neutralizing excess stomach acid and forming a protective barrier over the lining of the stomach and esophagus, which helps to reduce irritation and discomfort. Digene is available in tablet, liquid, and chewable forms and is typically taken as needed.

title: Paracetamol
description: Paracetamol is an analgesic and antipyretic medication used to alleviate mild to moderate pain such as headaches, toothaches, menstrual cramps, muscle aches, and reduce fever. It can also be used to lower fever associated with colds and flu. Paracetamol works by intervening in the body's pain and fever response.

title: Care Glycerin
description: Aspirin is a naturally occurring compound metabolized into acetylsalicylic acid when consumed. Acetylsalicylic acid is a nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drug (NSAID) commonly used to relieve pain, reduce inflammation, and lower fever. It is also used in low doses as a blood thinner to reduce the risk of heart attack and stroke in people at high risk. Aspirin works by inhibiting the production of prostaglandins, which are chemicals that promote inflammation, pain, and fever.

title: Difflam Throat Spray
description: Difflam is a throat spray used to alleviate symptoms such as throat pain and irritation. It has anti-inflammatory and analgesic properties. Difflam works by reducing inflammation in the oral cavity and soothing the throat tissue.

title: Optrex
description: Optrex is an eye drop used to relieve eye problems such as redness, itching, and irritation. Optrex is designed to moisturize and protect the eyes.

title: Lemsip-Max-Cold
description: Lemsip Max Cold is a medication used to relieve symptoms of colds and flu. Lemsip can help alleviate nasal congestion, sore throat, cough, and fever. It may also generally help the individual feel better.
